Welcome.Wel_H3BPMDes: Welcome to the H3 BPM management center. H3 BPM Management Center is H3 BPM development and testing, the implementation of the configuration, operation and maintenance of each unified management platform, in H3 BPM management center, you can possible graphical visualization, parametric approach, the minimum code of the enterprise's processes and business class, and the entire system maintenance and management.
Welcome.Wel_Home: You can manage your enterprise applications with H3 App Center. H3 Enterprise App combiles process/data models, reports and list view to one single app.
Welcome.Wel_LogDes: H3 BPM system logging user login logs, exception log, log business integration, organizational change log and mobile office using the log.
Welcome.Wel_BizBusDesc: Adapter and interface configuration processes data with external systems, service interaction
Welcome.Wel_BizRuleDesc: Configuration can be stripped out of the process complex business rules and processes to reduce complexity and improve maintainability
Welcome.Wel_BizWorkflowDes: Simulation testing to achieve the main process-related data, data models, processes, forms and processes of development and implementation
Welcome.Wel_BPADes: Implementation process of various types of report definitions, including process performance, process optimization, business statistics and analysis
Welcome.Wel_RMDes: Define report data sources, create tables, or create graphical cross-analysis reports
Welcome.Wel_AppsActivityDes: The process model, report model functions, including master data management, form input, process flow, statements, statistical analysis, and other custom functions, combined into one application.
Welcome.Wel_SettingsDes: Set various parameters to support operation
Welcome.Wel_OrganizationDes: H3 BPM organizational model with organization, person, group, groups, organizations and other rich elements of the post through the flexible use of these elements meet, including tree management, matrix management, virtual team management, reporting, and other multi-line management structure .
Welcome.Wel_SyncDes: Organizations to implement H3 BPM synchronization
Welcome.Wel_RoleDes: Define the user role of the enterprise
Welcome.Wel_Org_Des: Tree structure manages the organization, users, groups, and relationships between organizations, etc.
Welcome.Wel_BizBus_Des: H3 BPM service integration can register various interfaces and services to the system through the adapter provided by the system by default or self-developed, and provide the process data input and output call, process event trigger call and so on.
Welcome.Wel_BizServiceDes: A service established by an adapter to access an enterprise application system interface
Welcome.Wel_BizDatabaseDes: Configure H3 BPM access to all database links, support SQL SERVER / Oracle / MySql
Welcome.Wel_AdapterDes: Adapter that connects various types of interfaces in the enterprise internal application system
Welcome.Wel_BizRule_Des: H3 BPM business rules can define various business rules through the default or self-developed parser, and link with process data to implement rules and processes.
Welcome.Wel_BizRuleParserDes: The system's built-in rule parser, including scripts, selections, and collations
Welcome.Wel_BizRuleInstanceDes: Business rule instance created based on rule parser
Welcome.Wel_BizWorkflow_Des: The H3 BPM process model is the core function of the product. Through the definition of data, forms and processes, the process is modeled and run.
Welcome.Wel_MainDataDes: One of the data models is the basic data of the system, which can be customized or derived from external systems.
Welcome.Wel_DataModelDes: Data items can be customized or read from outside via business services
Welcome.Wel_FormModelDes: According to the data model automatically generated after the WEB designer can be visually adjusted, and can be further exported as ASP.net code through Visual Studio extension
Welcome.Wel_OperatingParamDes: Settings for the permissions of the process, the exception manager, the application's work calendar, etc.
Welcome.Wel_ProcessTemplateDes: Graphical drag, pull, and throw definitions, and provide a wealth of process parameters
Welcome.Wel_ProcessSimulationDes: Automate process testing through process use cases to automatically simulate operational processes
Welcome.Wel_RM_Des: The H3 BPM report model realizes the statistical analysis of processes and services through the rapid definition of two-step report data source definition and report template. At the same time, the H3 BPM reporting model provides a rich set of built-in reports that work out of the box.
Welcome.Wel_ReportDataSourceDes: Define report data sources, which can come from H3 BPM or other business systems
Welcome.Wel_ReportInstanceDes: Form or graphical cross-analysis report based on report data source
Welcome.Wel_AppsActivity_Des: The H3 BPM Application Center implements the definition of business application modules by combining forms and processes in the process model, reports in the report model, query lists in the data model, custom task and process functions built into the system, and custom functions.
Welcome.Wel_BusinessFormDes: System form or external form defined in the process package
Welcome.Wel_BusinessProcessDes: Business process defined in the process model
Welcome.Wel_DataQueryDes: Business data query and list display interface
Welcome.Wel_ReportAnalysisDes: Report instance defined by the associated report model module
Welcome.Wel_CustomToDoDes: Display custom to-do tasks, you can add business fields to display in the to-do list
Welcome.Wel_OperatingSystemDes: Independent business systems consisting of other functions, such as sales management, conference management, etc.
Welcome.Wel_Settings_Des: The H3 BPM system parameters centralize all system configuration options for configuration management by the implementer or system administrator.
Welcome.Wel_GeneralParametersDes: Set WeChat binding, APP push, file storage, system related parameters, etc.
Welcome.Wel_OrganizationAuthorityDes: Grant administrator privileges by organizational dimension
Welcome.Wel_MessageSettingsDes: Set the system message sending method, such as: SMS, email, WeChat, etc.
Welcome.Wel_WorkCalendarDes: Set up the system work calendar
Welcome.Wel_GlobalVariableDes: The environment variable is a global variable that the system runs.
Welcome.Wel_DelegateSettingDes: Authorized task authorization by the administrator
Welcome.Wel_SSODes: Set up a single sign-on system
